Titolo: Fu-un Bakumatsu-den

Anno: 2005

Descrizione: Fu-un Bakumatsu-den (風雲 幕末伝) is a Japanese PlayStation 2 game made in 2005 by Genki Co. as a follow-up to Fu-un Shinsengumi.  In 2009, it was remade for the PlayStation Portable as Fu-un Shinsengumi -Bakumatsu-den- Portable (風雲 新撰組‐幕末伝‐portable) by From Software.
As in the previous game, the player takes the role of a member of the Shinsengumi militia force.